{"tid":9102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉通貨膨脹率達720%","createTime":"2016-11-28T13:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T05:50:31.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a25cc666696cc32770b9aac3972a5ac617f19807","tid":9102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>委內瑞拉通膨720% 皮夾太小裝錢得用背包</strong><br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：2016/11/28 18:52<br />\n最新更新：2016/11/28 19:22<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/800/20161128/15005643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F800%2F20161128%2F15005643.jpg&h=aebe76fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南美委內瑞拉最近不容易看到有人付帳，還帶著皮夾錢包。今年通貨膨脹預估將狂飆720%，委國最大面額鈔票100玻利瓦（bolivar）在黑市淪為只值5美分。<br />\n（<a href=\"http://圖取自華盛頓郵報網站www.washingtonpost.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AA%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%9B%E9%A0%93%E9%83%B5%E5%A0%B1%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.washingtonpost.com&d=fSbu67zwg59zlzH2S6vVBMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=11f0006c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自華盛頓郵報網站www.washingtonpost.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社委內瑞拉卡拉卡斯28日綜合外電報導）南美委內瑞拉最近不容易看到有人付帳，還帶著皮夾錢包。今年通貨膨脹預估將狂飆720%，委國最大面額鈔票100玻利瓦（bolivar）在黑市淪為只值5美分。<br />\n<br />\n美國「華盛頓郵報」（Washington Post）報導，委國以石油收入為主的經濟崩潰，加上政府瘋狂印鈔票，幣值一洩千里，物價一路狂飆，<span style=\"color: red;\">當地居民因此得隨身攜帶為數龐大的鈔票，</span>皮夾太小裝不下，<strong>得動用手提包、腰包和背包才行。</strong><br />\n<br />\n卡拉卡斯1家販賣報紙、香菸和零食的小亭子老闆表示，他每天傍晚不動聲色的把面額10、20、50和100的玻利瓦的鈔票，裝入塑膠袋中，總金額約10萬玻利瓦（約新台幣1664元）。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉是犯罪率最高的國家之一，身懷大量的鈔票不安全。<br />\n<br />\n小亭子賣最好的是香菸，香菸價格從250玻利瓦一路漲到2000玻利瓦，2000玻利瓦現在黑市價值約1美元。賣出1包菸會收到20張100玻利瓦。<br />\n<br />\n幣值急遽縮水，代表從銀行的自動提款機（ATM）提款5美元，至少會領到100張100玻利瓦。某些ATM得每3小時補鈔，因為ATM可以容納的鈔票數量有限。由於補鈔不易，運作正常的ATM數量有限，四處可見排隊領錢人龍。<br />\n<br />\n大量現金攜帶不易，促使不少委內瑞拉人改以信用卡付款。1家不便透露姓名的咖啡店老闆表示，店裡90%收入來自電子支付。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉經濟智庫Econometrica總監賈西亞（Henkel Garcia）指出，電子支付在委內瑞拉逐漸普遍.線上支付可能大幅成長。（譯者：中央社劉淑琴）1051128<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201611280348-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201611280348-1.aspx&d=fSbu67zwg59zlzH2S6vVBMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=43be9334\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201611280348-1.aspx</a>[/quote]"},{"pid":"56d3261e9afa5404e1af87ec2277efbc70ef97f3","tid":9102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9b332d8ae337b9f3c3e5d7664f7b13ec77890f","tid":9102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0531d27e20ba90e6586841e9e207fd3cfe2abfd","tid":9102,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"聽講委內瑞拉好多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/120506_11a900156f6c227f784b62a14862613e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F120506_11a900156f6c227f784b62a14862613e.jpg&h=877fb294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機會嚟啦Plus仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1fab20d3393e53ac7321e1ad6714bf6c9e330a","tid":9102,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"點樣可以令個國家貨幣搞到咁？ 冇讀econ覺得自己好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2c3d7416808ed060a90e2ab5fcf3888b5f444f","tid":9102,"uid":16408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣可以令個國家貨幣搞到咁？ 冇讀econ覺得自己好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d61fff8ab940a9aff9727ed89811235c199ba6","tid":9102,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:45:01.000Z","msg":"超通漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f4e7820f07faa9b7fd00e40d9bac3364352150","tid":9102,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣可以令個國家貨幣搞到咁？ 冇讀econ覺得自己好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢哋行緊類似共產主義嘅制度，以前石油貴所以國家收入夠政府開支俾福利開支。但近排右油平左，政府收入少左，咪要瘋狂印錢補貼，結果咪惡性通貨膨脹囉<br />\n<br />\n利申工程撚，有錯唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}